reviewText: I'm half way thru week 2 and the instructor is still just repeating the same sentence over and over again. They only talk about how the course will change your life, but never get into the lessons or anything past introductions. After 2 weeks of hearing the instructor just talk about themselves and the course I just felt like I was in a fever dream not a class.

It had the potential to be a great course but turned out to be a potpourri of Greatest Hits of some business articles behind paywalls and some unconnected(!) random ramblings. There appears to be structure on the surface but it really does not work. Still happy that I took it. There were still few gems in the dust. D&I content appears to be very random and token.

This is an excellent way to understand one's role in influencing change by better understanding oneself, one's relationship in a team, and working collaboratively to make thoughtful priorities and strategies
New insights, very useful and practical.
I LOVE THIS COURSE. IT IS LIKE A MEDITATION JOURNEY
Very informative. So many life lessons.
Excellent!  Very informative with learnings that are easily applicable to any leadership role
